4<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n  <\/tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Exhibitor Table<\/td>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n  <\/tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Podcast interview on one of EMI\u2019s podcasts<\/td>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n  <\/tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Premium logo placement in high-visibility areas (e.g., coffee stations)<\/td>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n  <\/tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Digital ads: Inclusion in pre-event emails and posts<\/td>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n  <\/tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Two dedicated social media shout-outs before the event<\/td>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n  <\/tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Lead generation: Logo on our website linked to a site of your choice<\/td>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n  <\/tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Post-event mention in the recap email<\/td>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n  <\/tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Copies of Beyond PM Training: How to Build a Scalable AEC Project Management Ecosystem by Anthony Fasano<\/td>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>5<\/th>\n    <th>10<\/th>\n  <\/tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>1 additional Podcast interview, for a total of two interviews, on one of EMI\u2019s podcasts<\/td>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n  <\/tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Speaking opportunity: Concurrent or panel slot at the event, or the chance to moderate a session<\/td>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n  <\/tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Co-branding: Logo featured on lanyards and name badges<\/td>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n  <\/tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Exclusive booth or area for demos or hospitality<\/td>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u274c<\/th>\n    <th>\u2714<\/th>\n  <\/tr>\n  <tr>\n